urls.description: Starting 5th July 2022, we are extending our call center service hours to offer you more convenience and serve you better.

data.text: Great news! We’ve extended our call center service hours to serve you better. As of 5th July, you can reach our call center by phone between 8am & 8pm from Monday to Friday & 9am to 6pm on the weekends. To know more about our revamped servicing, visit https://t.co/zIsJsGYagK https://t.co/1SF6vOJTaO

On 4th June 2022, we celebrated 10 years of connecting Abuja to Paris and beyond on Air France. It was all pomp & color at the Air France airport check in area in Abuja. Thank you to all our customers. Here's to thousands of memories made & to many more years! https://t.co/o594PiQygz
